      <ul>
        <li><strong>v31 Temporal Memory</strong>: ordered, long-term memory stream.</li>
        <li><strong>v32â€“33 Motivation / Horizon</strong>: goals, milestones and priorities.</li>
        <li><strong>v34â€“38 Multi-Agent Kernel</strong>: orchestration of multiple AI agents.</li>
