        <li><strong>v36 Giving / Social Value</strong>: aligning revenue with contribution.</li>
        <li><strong>v37 Human Sovereignty</strong>: human approval and braking mechanisms.</li>
        <li><strong>v38â€“40 Unified Kernel</strong>: unified decision-making engine.</li>
        <li><strong>v50 Self-Diagnosis &amp; Healing</strong>: anomaly detection and repair.</li>
      </ul>
