      <h2>Chapter 6: Multi-Agent Workflows</h2>
      <p>
        On top of SCA, multiple AI agents take different roles:
        research, coding, review, safety auditing, and more.<br />
        They do not each have their own siloed memory; instead they act as
        limbs of the same external brain, sharing SCAâ€™s policies and memory.
      </p>
